highlights.text: “ENEMY” by TWICE is the highest new entry on Top Songs Hong Kong at #179.
“反對無效” by MC 張天賦 has been on Top Songs Hong Kong the longest, at 1519 days straight.
MC 張天賦 has the most spots on Top Songs Hong Kong. “東邪” is the highest at #13.
“到此為止” by Shiga Lin is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Hong Kong, up 50 spots at #119.
